As a global technology company and innovation leader in electrification, automation, and digitalization, Siemens supports sustainable industrialization. With our engineering expertise, our knowledge of numerous sectors, and our digital technology, we help our business partners across the entire value chain, from design to production, and from operations to maintenance. We believe in international partnerships as the key to innovation. A large percentage of our customers and suppliers are small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). We have officially adopted sustainability as an additional strategic imperative for our investment decisions.